  "description": "Erection for two additional storey of accommodation to increase the building from three storey to five storey and installation of additional windows in connection with creation of eight self-contained flats (retrospective). Proposed replacement of existing 4 x 3-bedroom and 3 x 2 bedroom flats with proposed 4 x 2-bedroom and 3 x 1 bedroom flats on first, second, third and fourth floors, and internal alterations to flats layout at first, second, third and fourth floors. Provision of refuse and cycle storage.",
  "lapsed_date": "04/10/2025",
